title: Nuclear Biological Chemical Weapons Safety Books Collection
description:
NBC Related Material Collection (Nuclear Biological Chemical Weapons Safety)

A collection of safety guides and field manuals on how to properly deal with nuclear, chemical, and biological weapons.

Topics include making shelters, treating injuries, decontamination, and otherwise making yourself safer.  There is some very good material in here; another torrent well worth downloading, storing away, and maybe even printing a few of the pdf's.
